view(class='container')
  view(class='usermotto')
    text(class='user-motto' bind:tap='gotoLogsPage') {{motto}}

  button(size='mini' bind:tap='increase') 在 Page 中增加 Count：{{count}}

  span 单向绑定：
  counter(number='{{count}}')

  span 双向绑定：
  counter(number.sync='{{count}}')

  demo(toast.sync='demoToast')
  button(size='mini' bind:tap='toggleDemoToast') 多层双向绑定，Page -> Demo -> Toast
